            <p>These five verbs are some of the most commonly used verbs, so you will need to familiarise yourself with
                them. If you are familiar with other Germanic languages, such as German, Dutch, Russian or Swedish,
                you'll notice that most of those verbs are also irregular in those languages.
                We'll explore the oddities of these verbs in detail throughout the coming topics. Let's take a closer
                look at the related verbs '<em>beon</em>' and '<em>wesan</em>' first.</p>
